li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Eigenschaften</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/arguments\"><code>Function.prototype.arguments</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/caller\"><code>Function.prototype.caller</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/displayName\"><code>Function.prototype.displayName</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/length\"><code>Function.prototype.length</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/name\"><code>Function.prototype.name</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/prototype\"><code>Function.prototype.prototype</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methoden</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/apply\"><code>Function.prototype.apply()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/bind\"><code>Function.prototype.bind()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/call\"><code>Function.prototype.call()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/toString\"><code>Function.prototype.toString()</code></a></li></ol></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Eigenschaften</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methoden</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Die <code><strong>includes()-</strong></code>Methode gibt an, ob ein String innerhalb eines anderen Strings gefunden wird und gibt dabei <code>true</code> oder <code>false</code> wieder.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code><var>str</var>.includes(<var>searchString</var>[, <var>position</var>])</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameter","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"searchstring\"><code>searchString</code></dt>\n <dd>Ein String, der innerhalb eines anderen Strings gesucht wird.</dd>\n <dt id=\"position\"><code>position</code></dt>\n <dd>Optional. Die Position innerhalb des besuchten Strings durch <code>searchString</code>; Standard ist 0.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"wertwiedergabe","title":"Wertwiedergabe","isH3":true,"content":"<p><strong><code>true</code></strong>, wenn der String den gesuchten String enthält, andernfalls <strong><code>false</code></strong>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beschreibung","title":"Beschreibung","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Diese Methode lässt dich feststellen, ob ein String einen anderen String beinhaltet.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"achtung_auf_groß-_kleinschreibung","title":"Achtung auf Groß-, Kleinschreibung","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Bei der <code>includes()</code>-Methode muss auf Groß- und Kleinschreibung geachtet werden.<br>\n Zum Beispiel gibt die folgende Darstellung <code>false</code> aus:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token string\">'Blue Whale'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">includes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'blue'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// gibt false wieder</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"einsatz_von_includes","title":"Einsatz von <code>includes()</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Sein oder nicht sein, das ist hier die Frage.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">includes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Sein'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>        <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">includes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Frage'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>       <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">includes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'nicht da'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>    <span class=\"token comment\">// false</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">includes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Sein'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>     <span class=\"token comment\">// false</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">includes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'SEIN'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>        <span class=\"token comment\">// false</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Einsatz von includes()"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"polyfill","title":"Polyfill","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Diese Methode wurde den ECMAScript 6 Spezifikationen hinzugefügt und könnte nicht in allen JavaScript-Umgebunden vorhanden sein. Jedoch kann man diesen Polyfill nutzen:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>prototype<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>includes<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>prototype<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">includes</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">search<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> start</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">'use strict'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">typeof</span> start <span class=\"token operator\">!==</span> <span class=\"token string\">'number'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      start <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>start <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> search<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length <span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">indexOf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>search<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> start<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!==</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikationen</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-string.prototype.includes\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'String.prototype.includes' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>erste Definition</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-string.prototype.includes\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'String.prototype.includes' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser-Kompatibilität","id":"browser-kompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.String.includes","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/includes/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"string.prototype.contains","title":"String.prototype.contains","isH3":false,"content":"<p>In Firefox 18 - 39 hieß diese Methode <code>contains()</code>. Es wurde zu <code>includes()</code> (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1102219\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;1102219</a>) wegen folgender Gründe umbenannt:<br>\n <br>\n Es wurde gemeldet, dass manche Webseiten, die MooTools 1.2 nutzen mit Firefox 17 nicht mehr funktionieren. Diese Version von MooTools kontrolliert, ob <code>String.prototype.contains()</code> existiert und, wenn nicht, fügt es seine eigene Funktion hinzu.<br>\n Mit der Einführung dieser Funktion in Firefox 17 wurde das Verhalten dieser Kontrolle geändert, sodass auf MooTools <code>String.prototype.contains()</code> basierender Code funktionsunfähig wurde.<br>\n Aufgrund dessen wurde die Implementierung in Firefox 17 <a href=\"https://hg.mozilla.org/releases/mozilla-aurora/rev/086db97198a8\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">abgeschaltet </a>und <code>String.prototype.contains()</code> war in Firefox 18 nutzbar. Ermöglicht wurde dies durch die <a href=\"http://mootools.net/blog/2013/02/19/mootools-1-2-6-released\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Veröffentlichung von MooTools Version 1.2.6.</a></p>\n\n<p>MooTools 1.3 erzwingt die Nutzung der eigenen Version von <code>String.prototype.contains()</code>, demnach sollten Webseiten, die abhängig davon sind, weiterhin funktionieren. Beachte jedoch, dass sich die <a href=\"http://mootools.net/core/docs/1.3.2/Types/String#String-method:-contains\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MooTools 1.3 Signatur </a>von der ECMAScript 6 Signatur für diese Methode unterscheidet.</p>\n\n<p>Später änderte <a href=\"https://github.com/mootools/mootools-core/blob/master/Docs/Types/String.md#note\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MooTools 1.5+ die Signatur, um sie dem ES2015 Standard anzupassen.</a></p>\n\n<p><br>\n In Firefox 48 wurde <code>String.prototype.contains()</code> entfernt. Nutze lediglich <code>String.prototype.includes()</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array/includes\"><code>Array.prototype.includes()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypedArray/includes\"><code>TypedArray.prototype.includes()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/indexOf\"><code>String.prototype.indexOf()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/lastIndexOf\"><code>String.prototype.lastIndexOf()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/startsWith\"><code>String.prototype.startsWith()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/endsWith\"><code>String.prototype.endsWith()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beschreibung","id":"beschreibung"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Polyfill","id":"polyfill"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browser-Kompatibilität","id":"browser-kompatibilität"},{"text":"String.prototype.contains","id":"string.prototype.contains"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Die includes()-Methode gibt an, ob ein String innerhalb eines anderen Strings gefunden wird und gibt dabei true oder false wieder.","popularity":0.0013,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"String.prototype.includes()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"String.prototype.includes()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"String.prototype.includes()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"String.prototype.includes()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"String.prototype.includes()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"String.prototype.includes()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"String.prototype.includes()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"String.prototype.includes()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/string/includes","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/string/includes/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"JavaScript-Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"Globale Objekte"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String","title":"String"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/includes","title":"String.prototype.includes()"}],"pageTitle":"String.prototype.includes() - JavaScript | MDN","noIndexing":false}}